# Realtors360 CRM — Windsurf Rules
# Source of truth: .claude/agent-playbook.md + AGENTS.md
# Same rules as .cursorrules — see that file for full details

Read `.claude/agent-playbook.md` before every task.
Read `.claude/quick-reference.md` for the checklist.

Hard constraints: No `any`, no inline styles, Server Actions for mutations,
RLS on every table, multi-tenant via `getAuthenticatedTenantClient()`,
Zod validation, never push to main/dev directly, no PII in prompts.

Architecture: Next.js 16 + Supabase + TypeScript. Path alias @/ = src/.
CSS: lf-* classes. force-dynamic on live pages. revalidatePath() after mutations.

Every feature needs: use-case doc, tests, PR with classification block.
Git: branch from dev, PR back to dev, conventional commits.
